Inverse Association between Fruit and Vegetable Intake and All-Cause Mortality: 
Japan Public Health Center-Based Prospective Study.

Sahashi Y(1)(2)(3), Goto A(1)(4), Takachi R(5), Ishihara J(6), Kito K(5)(7), 
