A systematic review of economic evaluations of preoperative smoking cessation 
for preventing surgical complications.

McCaffrey N(1), Higgins J(2), Greenhalgh E(3), White SL(3), Graves N(4), Myles 
PS(5), Cunningham JE(6), Dean E(3), Doncovio S(7), Briggs L(8), Lal A(9).

Author information:
(1)Deakin University, Deakin Health Economics, Institute for Health 
Transformation, School of Health and Social Development, Geelong, Victoria, 
Australia; Cancer Council Victoria, Melbourne, Victoria, Australia. Electronic 
address: nikki.mccaffrey@deakin.edu.au.
(2)Deakin University, Geelong, Australia.
(3)Cancer Council Victoria, Melbourne, Victoria, Australia.
(4)Health Services & Systems Research, Duke-NUS Medical School, Singapore.
(5)Department of Anaesthesiology and Perioperative Medicine, Alfred Hospital and 
