Objectives: People living with HIV (PWH) have seen reduction in HIV-associated 
morbidity and increase in near-normal life expectancy, yet unhealthy alcohol use 
poses substantial risks to older as well as younger adults. Further research 
regarding age-associated physical and mental health concerns among PWH who drink 
