Nephrology Dialysis Transplantation, and Age and Ageing. © The Author(s) 2022. 
Published by Oxford University Press on behalf of the ERA and the British 
Geriatrics Society. All rights reserved. The articles are identical except for 
minor stylistic and spelling differences in keeping with each journal's style. 
Either citation can be used when citing this article.

