PMID: 35768248 [Indexed for MEDLINE]


905. Sci Rep. 2022 Jun 29;12(1):11004. doi: 10.1038/s41598-022-14784-9.

Reducing the energy cost of walking with low assistance levels through optimized 
hip flexion assistance from a soft exosuit.

Kim J(#)(1), Quinlivan BT(#)(1), Deprey LA(1)(2), Arumukhom Revi D(1)(3)(4), 
Eckert-Erdheim A(1), Murphy P(1), Orzel D(1), Walsh CJ(5).

Author information:
(1)John A. Paulson School of Engineering and Applied Sciences, Harvard 
University, Boston, 02134, USA.
(2)School of Life Sciences, Swiss Federal Institute of Technology (EPFL), 
